In the MATTER OF the TERESA KASPARBAUER REVOCABLE LIVING TRUST, Marie Eischeid, Marguerite Nielsen, Teresa Smith, Annette Firkus, Kathleen Kasparbauer, and Mary Smith, Defendants-Appellants. No. 17-1129 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

The defendants appeal from the district court's grant of partial summary judgment in favor of the plaintiffs. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
